import React from 'react'; import './card.css'; import line from './line.png'; class Card extends React.Component{ onSubmitClick=()=>{ fetch('http://localhost:3001/saveCovSimple',{ method:'post', headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'}, body:JSON.stringify({ userId:this.props.myId, covSId:this.props.idc }) }) .then(response=>response.json()) .then(user=>{ this.props.onRouteChange('save') }) } render(){ const {name,lastname,email,userid,number,depart,arrive,prix,date,hd,ha,onPayment,bagage,nbrplacedispo,typevehicule,confortvoiture,rating,id}=this.props; return (

{name} {lastname}

{rating}/5

+212 {number}

{date}

{depart}

{hd}

{arrive}

{ha}

{bagage}
Voiture : {typevehicule}
Place : {nbrplacedispo}
Confort : {confortvoiture}

{prix} DH

) } } export default Card;
